text: Gumerovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Gorkovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 184 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Kushnarenkovo, 6 km from Ilikovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Gumerovo, Kushnarenkovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
